record.title: ADJOURNMENT UNTIL WEDNESDAY, NOVEMBER 19, 2008, AT 9:30 A.M.
record.narrative:
ADJOURNMENT UNTIL WEDNESDAY, NOVEMBER 19, 2008, AT 9:30 A.M. -- (Senate - November 17, 2008)

[Page: S10602]

speaking.paragraph: If there is no further business to come before the Senate, I ask unanimous consent that it stand adjourned under the previous order.

record.narrative: There being no objection, the Senate, at 6:03 p.m., adjourned until Wednesday, November 19, 2008, at 9:30 a.m.
